<br>
Okay, go to the Centra Ruins.  There was another mission to do here.  Do that first and then go back.  You'll notice that all you'll be fighting, for the most part, are small Tonberries.  Make sure you have the enc-all thing junctioned, if you have it, because you have to do all this in 20 minutes or less.  YOu have to fight at least 18 of those small Tonberries first.  The best thing to do is make sure someone has Diablo and they have 100% compatibility with him.  Then make someone repeatedly cast Haste on the person with Diable, and then just keep summoning Diablo on the Tonberries.  After you've beaten 18 (it took about 22 for me) the King Tonberry will appear.  Kill him and you'll get the GF.  But don't use Diablo on the king because it doesn't do anything.  I can't remember how I killed the King TOnbery though. <p><font face="Verdana" size="2">
