<br>
There are four places to acquire four Gfs, you will have to this in order to acquire them.<br>
1)Sentura ruins - GF King Tonberry<br>
2)Cactaur Island - GF Sabotander<br>
3)Warship Island - GF Bahamut<br>
4)Warship Island - GF Eden<br>
So like I said in order, which means you won't be able to acquire Sabotander if your did not defeat King Tonberry or in other words you can only get Sabotander, after you defeat Tonberry. So fight these Gf monsters in order. <br>
<br>
Since Tonberry is the first one you will have to fight, here is little more help:<br>
Before you fight King Tonberry, you will have to defeat 20 Tonberries. After 20th Tonberry is defeated the King Tonberry will appear.<br>
Other little Tonberries: HP 22,600 (They are quite weak against Diablo)<br>
King Tonberry's HP is about 95,000<br>
